enes was found at subsequent shifts to either nectarivory or frugivory. Thus, neotropical noctilionoids that use visual cues for identifying food and roosts, as well as for orientation, were effectively preadapted, with subsequent molecular adaptations in nectar\u2010feeding lineages and the subfamily Stenodermatinae of fig\u2010eating bats fine\u2010tuning pre\u2010existing visual adaptations for specialized purposes.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Davies, Kalina T. J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Yohe, Laurel R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Almonte, Jesus", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "S\u00e1nchez, Miluska K. R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rengifo, Edgardo M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Dumont, Elizabeth R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sears, Karen E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "D\u00e1valos, Liliana M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rossiter, Stephen J.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/76c3855fa72bc88e8c67e9e9e278cff4", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/d9e279eb917c3b0d9fe0249470d71ada60d08e8594c35d4e2c3f76be9978d707", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/UWLCX2UH", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/UWLCX2UH", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/4a21baffde0978110ddbf8122852ed2c!/b201141-203605", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["